<HEADLINE>  Kosovo Kids Go Back to School </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PRISTINA, Yugoslavia (AP) -- Thousands of Kosovo students  
returned to school today, the first time pupils in the province 
have been able to attend class since NATO launched its war against 
Yugoslavia five months ago. 
</P>
