	Sept. 7: Singer Gloria Gaynor is 50. Singer Chrissie Hynde of  
the Pretenders is 48. Actress Julie Kavner is 48. Actor Corbin 
Bernsen is 45. 
</P>
<P>
	Sept. 8: Comedian Sid Caesar is 77. Actress Heather Thomas is  
42. Musician David Steele of Fine Young Cannibals is 39. Actor 
