<HEADLINE>  Dennis Cuts Hatteras Island in Half </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NAGS HEAD, N.C. (AP) -- Tropical storm Dennis weakened today and  
began drifting back toward North Carolina's Outer Banks, where its 
first pass had sliced Hatteras Island in half and isolated 
